<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <%- include('partials/head') %>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
   

    <!-- Services Start -->
    <div class="container-fluid py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="text-center mx-auto mb-5" style="max-width: 500px;">
                <h5 class="d-inline-block text-primary text-uppercase border-bottom border-5">Services</h5>
                <h1 class="display-4">Excellent Medical Services</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="row g-5">
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                    <div
                        class="service-item bg-light rounded d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center text-center">
                        <div class="service-icon mb-4">
                            <i class="fa fa-2x fa-user-md text-white"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="mb-3">Emergency Care</h4>
                        <p class="m-0">In urgent situations, our emergency care services allow you to connect with a qualified medical professional quickly.</p>
                        <a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary rounded-pill" href="/service-details">
                            <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                    <div
                        class="service-item bg-light rounded d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center text-center">
                        <div class="service-icon mb-4">
                            <i class="fa fa-2x fa-procedures text-white"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="mb-3">Operation & Surgery</h4>
                        <p class="m-0"> Our network of experienced surgeons can provide insight into potential procedures, discuss risks, and help prepare you for surgery if needed. </p>
                        <a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary rounded-pill" href="/service-details">
                            <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                    <div
                        class="service-item bg-light rounded d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center text-center">
                        <div class="service-icon mb-4">
                            <i class="fa fa-2x fa-stethoscope text-white"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="mb-3">Outdoor Checkup</h4>
                        <p class="m-0">Our healthcare professionals can provide tips for injury prevention, managing allergies, and overall wellness in nature.</p>
                        <a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary rounded-pill" href="/service-details">
                            <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                    <div
                        class="service-item bg-light rounded d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center text-center">
                        <div class="service-icon mb-4">
                            <i class="fa fa-2x fa-ambulance text-white"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="mb-3">Ambulance Service</h4>
                        <p class="m-0">When emergencies strike, getting to a medical facility quickly can be crucial. HealingNet partners with reliable ambulance services to ensure that you receive timely transport in critical situations.</p>
                        <a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary rounded-pill" href="/service-details">
                            <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                    <div
                        class="service-item bg-light rounded d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center text-center">
                        <div class="service-icon mb-4">
                            <i class="fa fa-2x fa-pills text-white"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="mb-3">Medicine & Pharmacy</h4>
                        <p class="m-0">Managing your prescriptions has never been easier. Through HealingNet, you can consult with our healthcare providers regarding necessary medications. </p>
                        <a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary rounded-pill" href="/service-details">
                            <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                    <div
                        class="service-item bg-light rounded d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center text-center">
                        <div class="service-icon mb-4">
                            <i class="fa fa-2x fa-microscope text-white"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="mb-3">Blood Testing</h4>
                        <p class="m-0">Understanding your health through regular testing is essential. HealingNet collaborates with certified labs to provide blood testing services that are easy to access. </p>
                        <a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary rounded-pill" href="/service-details">
                            <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Services End -->


    <!-- Appointment Start -->
    <div class="container-fluid bg-primary my-5 py-5">
        <div class="container py-5">
            <div class="row gx-5">
                <div class="col-lg-6 mb-5 mb-lg-0">
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <h5 class="d-inline-block text-white text-uppercase border-bottom border-5">Appointment
                        </h5>
                        <h1 class="display-4">Make An Appointment For Your Family</h1>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-white mb-5">At HealingNet, scheduling an appointment has never been easier. Our user-friendly online platform allows you to book appointments at your convenience, ensuring that you can access the care you need without the hassle of traditional office visits. 
                    </p>
                    <a class="btn btn-dark rounded-pill py-3 px-5 me-3" href="">Find Doctor</a>
                    <a class="btn btn-outline-dark rounded-pill py-3 px-5" href="/appointment">Read More</a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="bg-white text-center rounded p-5">
                        <h1 class="mb-4">Book An Appointment</h1>
                        <form>
                            <div class="row g-3">
                                <div class="col-12 col-sm-6">
                                <select class="form-select bg-light border-0" style="height: 55px;">
                                    <%- include('partials/department') %>
                                </select>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-12 col-sm-6">
                                    <select class="form-select bg-light border-0" style="height: 55px;">
                                        <option selected>Select Doctor</option>
                                        <option value="1">Doctor 1</option>
                                        <option value="2">Doctor 2</option>
                                        <option value="3">Doctor 3</option>
                                    </select>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-12 col-sm-6">
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control bg-light border-0"
                                        placeholder="Your Name" style="height: 55px;">
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-12 col-sm-6">
                                    <input type="email" class="form-control bg-light border-0"
                                        placeholder="Your Email" style="height: 55px;">
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-12 col-sm-6">
                                    <div class="date" id="date" data-target-input="nearest">
                                        <input type="text"
                                            class="form-control bg-light border-0 datetimepicker-input"
                                            placeholder="Date" data-target="#date" data-toggle="datetimepicker"
                                            style="height: 55px;">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-12 col-sm-6">
                                    <div class="time" id="time" data-target-input="nearest">
                                        <input type="text"
                                            class="form-control bg-light border-0 datetimepicker-input"
                                            placeholder="Time" data-target="#time" data-toggle="datetimepicker"
                                            style="height: 55px;">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-12">
                                    <button class="btn btn-primary w-100 py-3" type="submit">Make An
                                        Appointment</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Appointment End -->


    <!-- Testimonial Start -->
    <div class="container-fluid py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="text-center mx-auto mb-5" style="max-width: 500px;">
                <h5 class="d-inline-block text-primary text-uppercase border-bottom border-5">Testimonial</h5>
                <h1 class="display-4">Patients Say About Our Services</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-lg-8">
                    <div class="owl-carousel testimonial-carousel">
                        <div class="testimonial-item text-center">
                            <div class="position-relative mb-5">
                                <img class="img-fluid rounded-circle mx-auto" src="img/testimonial-1.jpg"
                                    alt="">
                                <div class="position-absolute top-100 start-50 translate-middle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center bg-white rounded-circle"
                                    style="width: 60px; height: 60px;">
                                    <i class="fa fa-quote-left fa-2x text-primary"></i>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <p class="fs-4 fw-normal">"HealingNet has been a lifesaver for me. The online platform made it so easy to book appointments, and the care I received was top-notch. Highly recommend!"  </p>
                            <hr class="w-25 mx-auto">
                            <h3> Jane Smith</h3>
                            <h6 class="fw-normal text-primary mb-3">Software Engineer</h6>
                        </div>
                        <div class="testimonial-item text-center">
                            <div class="position-relative mb-5">
                                <img class="img-fluid rounded-circle mx-auto" src="img/testimonial-2.jpg"
                                    alt="">
                                <div class="position-absolute top-100 start-50 translate-middle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center bg-white rounded-circle"
                                    style="width: 60px; height: 60px;">
                                    <i class="fa fa-quote-left fa-2x text-primary"></i>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <p class="fs-4 fw-normal"> "The doctors at HealingNet are incredibly knowledgeable and compassionate. I felt truly cared for and supported throughout my treatment."</p>
                            <hr class="w-25 mx-auto">
                            <h3>John Ben</h3>
                            <h6 class="fw-normal text-primary mb-3">Teacher</h6>
                        </div>
                        <div class="testimonial-item text-center">
                            <div class="position-relative mb-5">
                                <img class="img-fluid rounded-circle mx-auto" src="img/testimonial-3.jpg"
                                    alt="">
                                <div class="position-absolute top-100 start-50 translate-middle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center bg-white rounded-circle"
                                    style="width: 60px; height: 60px;">
                                    <i class="fa fa-quote-left fa-2x text-primary"></i>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <p class="fs-4 fw-normal">"I had a wonderful experience with HealingNet. The convenience of online scheduling and the quality of care I received were exceptional." </p>
                            <hr class="w-25 mx-auto">
                            <h3>Blessing James</h3>
                            <h6 class="fw-normal text-primary mb-3"> Graphic Designer</h6>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Testimonial End -->


    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

</body>

</html>